 of ceritinib with potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitors should generally be avoided.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/34425/', '', 'Lamivudine, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Velpatasvir, Dolutegravir, Oseltamivir, Acyclovir, More', 'Futibatinib, Alpelisib, Lenvatinib, Trametinib, Vandetanib, Afatinib, Dacomitinib, Tivozanib, Sorafenib', 1767369485);
